name: Hunter Biden
summary: Hunter Biden, the son of U.S. President Joe Biden, has been found guilty in a federal gun case. A jury convicted him on all three felony counts, including lying about his drug use on a federal form when he purchased a gun in 2018. Biden's conviction comes after a highly publicized trial that attracted significant media attention. President Biden has stated that he will not pardon his son, who now faces potential jail time. The case has sparked debate about the prosecution's decision to pursue charges against Biden, with some arguing that it was politically motivated.

summary: Tragic news has emerged as the body of British TV doctor Michael Mosley has been discovered in Greece, confirming the worst fears of his family and colleagues.
